headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of Cintas (CTAS)
summary: Since July 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 99.3%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, Cintas has surged 224% to $218.87 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 16% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 9.7%.
